<span id="freeTextContainer14867594129358402703">A cast of unlikable characters doing terrible things to one another. This could have been a 5 star read for me but for the life of me I can&apos;t understand the control one character has over every one else that they came in contact with. Men and woman alike would practically lie down and die for this guy and I just didn&apos;t get it. He didn&apos;t come across as charming or charismatic so I&apos;m a little perplexed. However the writing is outrageously good and the short cliff hanging chapters were done to perf</span>
  <span id="freeText14867594129358402703" style="display:none">A cast of unlikable characters doing terrible things to one another. This could have been a 5 star read for me but for the life of me I can't understand the control one character has over every one else that they came in contact with. Men and woman alike would practically lie down and die for this guy and I just didn't get it. He didn't come across as charming or charismatic so I'm a little perplexed. However the writing is outrageously good and the short cliff hanging chapters were done to perfection. Even with my one complaint aside I was compelled to read this baby to the end and I did it quickly so that has to say something about the authors talent. I will definitely grab her next book. 3.5 stars!</span>
