<span id="freeTextContainer17562040910643974708">This was a dark character study that I was into from page 1. I found the characters (some likeable, some not) and their actions fascinating in a &quot;fly on the wall&quot; type of way...glad that I would never be in their situation. The ending, while satisfying on some levels...and clever, was way too abrupt. I feel like the reader deserves to know the aftermath. Still a solid 4.</span>
  <span id="freeText17562040910643974708" style="display:none">This was a dark character study that I was into from page 1. I found the characters (some likeable, some not) and their actions fascinating in a "fly on the wall" type of way...glad that I would never be in their situation. The ending, while satisfying on some levels...and clever, was way too abrupt. I feel like the reader deserves to know the aftermath. Still a solid 4.</span>
