<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11098697846541321013">Layne Fargo writes thrillers about angry women. She’s the author of the feminist psychological thriller novels THEY NEVER LEARN and TEMPER (both available now from Simon &amp; Schuster’s Scout Press imprint) and coauthor of the forthcoming Audible Original YOUNG RICH WIDOWS. She also co-created, co-hosts, and produces the podcast Unlikeable Female Characters on Lit Hub Radio. Layne was selected as a P</span>
  <span id="freeText11098697846541321013" style="display:none">Layne Fargo writes thrillers about angry women. She’s the author of the feminist psychological thriller novels THEY NEVER LEARN and TEMPER (both available now from Simon &amp; Schuster’s Scout Press imprint) and coauthor of the forthcoming Audible Original YOUNG RICH WIDOWS. She also co-created, co-hosts, and produces the podcast Unlikeable Female Characters on Lit Hub Radio. Layne was selected as a Pitch Wars mentee in 2017 and has since served as a Pitch Wars mentor three times. She lives in Chicago with her partner and their pets, where she enjoys long walks in the cemetery and spending all her money at indie bookstores.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="11098697846541321013" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

